title: Beverly Hills 90210 5x03 - A Clean Slate
description:
Season 5, Episode 3: A Clean Slate

Original Air Date: 21 September 1994

Josh helps Brandon run for student body president who shines at a debate. But a scandal comes up when an article written the previous year by Josh, but never published, which details Brandon&#039;s tutoring of D&#039;Shawn whom took rigged tests surfaces which threatens to tarnish Brandon&#039;s reputation. Donna asks Clare (now attending C.U. as a sophomore) to move into the beach front apartment to help pay the rent. But Clare brings a bad snoring habit with her. Meanwhile, Valerie secretly decides to pursue Dylan after finding Brenda&#039;s mementos of him in the Walsh garage, and begins hanging out at the pool hall where Dylan also drinks and hangs out.
